  "id": 6998,
  "name": "Masters of the Night-Wind",
  "desc": "<p>One of the six tribes of Natlan, also known as Mictlan. They are famous for their predictions and rituals to amplify the ability to communicate with the Night Kingdom and the Wayob.</p>",
