                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7495,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/24/237301566/7af24ba165ce8b89d310affbb18b4284_5428910278125549425.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Sanhaj",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A legendary Border Master of the Masters of the Night-Wind whose astonishing magic once repelled the dark cataclysm during the Battle of the Mare Jivari. His companion was Mahamba, the most enigmatic of the Iktomisaurs.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ayizu",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Chief of the Masters of the Night-Wind, who fought alongside",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7417,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/03/237301566/1a328d36a9cee6e5e2f7918ecb8d3637_8482852792156418172.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Il Capitano",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "500 years ago. Although many people viewed",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4811,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/11/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_7086984801760748.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Khaenri'ah",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "as the cause of the tragedy, Ayizu was kind to Thrain and helped him in his time of need. In his final moments, Ayizu told the Sentinel Knight about the Gnosis' ability to reconstruct the Ley Lines.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Liriwu",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A young mystic who went to",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7288,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Ochkanatlan",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "along with the Adventurers' group.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Kuntur",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Son of Qoyllor who lived on the star and a mortal, Ukuku. He is also known as \"Kuntur, Unloved of the Sun.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Huitzilin",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Huitzilin was a great shaman and Citlali's friend, who lived 200 years ago. She is famous for the Battle of Seven Colors, in which she used a mysterious color to construct a maze and trap the enemies inside.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7292,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/22/237301566/2bb789cd775d34ee2ba33457f5f9f332_782447097802699655.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Biram",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Tribal chief",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7300,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/26/151578876/188578a56ba75d147d6c8a14285e4a77_443914870928659383.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Citlali",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Chief Priestess and tribal elder, who has lived for over 200 years. She created the Spiritspeaker Stone — an artifact that can be used to communicate with the Wayob.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Great Tlapopoctiztetl",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Iktomisaur Elder, a living totem among the Masters of the Night-Wind. He was Huitzilin's companion under the name Claw.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7079,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Ororon",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A hero of the Masters of the Night Wind, who has been acknowledged by his Ancient Name",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Chikya",
